1
00:00:08,150 --> 00:00:14,590
♫ I just came from the forest not yet awake looking like a ginseng fairy ♫

2
00:00:14,590 --> 00:00:20,940
♫ I’m full of skills, I broke into the Martial Arts World alone ♫

3
00:00:20,940 --> 00:00:26,520
♫ I believe in destiny, looked everywhere but nobody specified what it is ♫

4
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:33,850
♫ Once again, I have hope and expectation of love yet who is my destiny is unknown ♫

5
00:00:33,850 --> 00:00:39,810
♫ See, turns out that destiny has always been waiting for me ♫

6
00:00:39,810 --> 00:00:45,740
♫ I believe that love really exists ♫

7
00:00:45,740 --> 00:00:52,290
♫ Take a look at me, I’m open and candid, careful, and never doubting love ♫

8
00:00:52,290 --> 00:00:59,400
♫ Although I fan the flames and cause trouble everywhere, I came to the world just to ask about the whereabouts of love ♫

9
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:02,530
♫ How do I find the ripple effect of my destiny? ♫

10
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:05,770
♫ What are the consciences of the proud me? ♫

11
00:01:05,770 --> 00:01:08,330
♫ Why bother worrying too much? ♫

12
00:01:08,330 --> 00:01:13,500
♫ I just know that wherever I go, you will be there with me ♫

13
00:01:19,570 --> 00:01:24,370
[Wu Lin Heroes]

14
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:29,050
[Episode 17]

15
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:37,159
We seem to be the only two people left between Heaven and Earth.

16
00:01:38,139 --> 00:01:40,239
Why aren't you awake yet?

17
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:44,860
It's all right if you don't wake up.

18
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:47,539
As long as you are by my side, all is well.

19
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:03,460
I'm still alive?

20
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:05,160
What is this nonsense?

21
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:08,340
I'm with you, and I'll make sure you'll live beyond 100.

22
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:14,320
Does your head still ache?

23
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:18,580
If you are fine, I'm fine.

24
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:20,480
Therefore,

25
00:02:21,379 --> 00:02:24,868
why don't you take a bite? You will recover really fast.

26
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:30,059
If I take a bite of you, what will happen to you?

27
00:02:30,059 --> 00:02:32,939
Nothing much. I'll recover by tomorrow.

28
00:02:32,939 --> 00:02:35,959
Have you already guessed? I'm indeed that Ginseng Fairy.

29
00:02:35,959 --> 00:02:38,455
What are you worried about?

30
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:42,292
I don't want to bite into your flesh.

31
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:53,360
Don't move. Didn't you say you couldn't feel my heartbeat?

32
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,591
That's because I don't have a heart.

33
00:02:55,591 --> 00:02:57,499
So you don't need to treat me as if I were a mortal.

34
00:02:57,499 --> 00:02:59,846
Just feel free to bite.

35
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:08,000
I guarantee that I'll really be fine if you take a bite.

36
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:10,159
Then...

37
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,759
Then, what will happen to your real form?

38
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:15,756
There'll be a piece missing from my real form, but it's fine.

39
00:03:17,612 --> 00:03:21,336
Before I met you, I was buried in the Changliu Mountain

40
00:03:21,336 --> 00:03:25,339
for 1,000 years to transform into a human form. You were the first person I met.

41
00:03:25,339 --> 00:03:27,800
I went to the valley and saw you practice swordplay and read books.

42
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:30,078
I was the one who saved you in the ancient tomb.

43
00:03:30,078 --> 00:03:31,680
I was really naive at that time.

44
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:35,120
I mean, I was too innocent and kind.

45
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,599
I was afraid that you'd die of injuries.

46
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:39,800
So I gave you half of my rootlet.

47
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:43,940
It's because I lost this half of a rootlet that I lost my memory.

48
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:47,789
My hair is transformed from the rootlets.

49
00:03:47,789 --> 00:03:51,919
That's why whenever you are injured, my head would ache.

50
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,460
The rootlets have a restorative effect.

51
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:56,479
But after all, you only have a half rootlet.

52
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:58,819
You are injured too severely this time.

53
00:03:58,819 --> 00:04:00,980
Those pursuers are still hunting us down.

54
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:02,659
If you don't take a bite from me,

55
00:04:02,659 --> 00:04:05,560
you won't be able to recover fast.

56
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,140
Oh, yes.

57
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:12,599
- What about your previous resurrection?
- Since I don't have a heart,

58
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:16,079
my breathing and pulse only temporarily stopped.

59
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:19,280
To me, that's not a real death.

60
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:21,621
It's like hibernation.

61
00:04:21,621 --> 00:04:24,939
My real form is the king of herbs, and it has a very strong vitality.

62
00:04:24,939 --> 00:04:29,205
No matter how severely I'm injured, I can revive again.

63
00:04:29,205 --> 00:04:31,795
All right then. You should have no more doubt now.

64
00:04:31,795 --> 00:04:33,879
Just take a bite!

65
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:37,600
What about those injuries you suffered at Tang Sect?

66
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:40,620
You are a miracle physician, so you should know the contraindications for ginseng.

67
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:43,418
That time, I mistakenly ate hellebore.

68
00:04:43,418 --> 00:04:46,779
That soup was meant for Tang Huan to induce vomiting.

69
00:04:46,779 --> 00:04:50,000
I was too careful and insisted on drinking the same soup.

70
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:54,060
That's why I suffered a backlash, lost my spiritual power, and even turned ugly.

71
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:56,860
Forget that. Let's not waste time. Hurry and bite.

72
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:58,420
Here.

73
00:05:00,620 --> 00:05:02,320
But...

74
00:05:03,659 --> 00:05:06,580
A ginseng will look ugly with a chunk of it missing.

75
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:08,060
Remember where we are.

76
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:12,979
You should worry about your own life right now instead of whether my real form will look ugly.

77
00:05:12,979 --> 00:05:17,360
Both are them are equally important to me.

78
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:20,219
When I take a bite, you will feel the pain.

79
00:05:20,219 --> 00:05:23,120
If a chunk is missing from you, I'll feel bad.

80
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,680
But, if you don't take a bite from me,

81
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:29,200
I alone won't be able to deal with those pursuers once they get here.

82
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:34,940
WIthout me dragging you down, you can run away faster.

83
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:38,420
You haven't been to the western region, have you?

84
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:41,120
If you want, you should visit there.

85
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,660
The western region has beautiful scenery,

86
00:05:43,660 --> 00:05:45,700
many delicious foods,

87
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:48,679
and, most importantly, no one will know you there.

88
00:05:48,679 --> 00:05:50,759
No one will hunt you down to kill you.

89
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:55,460
Besides, you can find your perfect partner there.

90
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:57,239
I don't know the way.

91
00:05:57,239 --> 00:05:59,933
I want you to take me there.

92
00:05:59,933 --> 00:06:02,419
Together we can go anywhere.

93
00:06:02,419 --> 00:06:05,299
You traversed north and south previously for many years.

94
00:06:05,299 --> 00:06:09,839
You don't know the way? All the flowers and plants will show you the way.

95
00:06:10,539 --> 00:06:12,960
What are you doing by talking about all this now?

96
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,909
Are you entrusting your last will?

97
00:06:14,909 --> 00:06:18,519
If you would simply take a bite, we can both live and live well.

98
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:20,879
You still haven't told me you love me.

99
00:06:20,879 --> 00:06:23,300
I absolutely won't take a bite from you.

100
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:26,719
Don't hurt yourself for me.

101
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:29,900
Actually...

102
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:38,199
I told you to bite, but you won't. You forced me to do it myself.

103
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:41,020
Don't you know it hurts more when I bite myself?

104
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:47,830
♫ One day, one night, a pair that is inseparable ♫

105
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:50,700
♫ Day and night, I’ll protect you unconditionally ♫

106
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:54,070
♫ How many times have we been through life and death? ♫

107
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:56,880
♫ Because you are by my side ♫

108
00:06:56,880 --> 00:07:00,580
♫ All my misfortunes becomes understated ♫

109
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:03,880
♫ After many upheavals, our love hasn’t diminished ♫

110
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:07,230
♫ Just like the day we first met ♫

111
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:15,410
♫ With every passing year, our longings for each other are stacked into eternity ♫

112
00:07:15,410 --> 00:07:27,030
♫ The road gradually becomes farther, we will abide by our long-ago promise to be together forever ♫

113
00:07:36,339 --> 00:07:40,239
Bai Yue!

114
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,530
Bai Yue!

115
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:44,080
Here I am.

116
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:54,599
Where did you go? Why did you disappear without a word?

117
00:07:54,599 --> 00:07:58,119
Have you recovered? I was scared out of my wits.

118
00:07:58,119 --> 00:07:59,639
What's this you, you, you again?

119
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:02,459
I already said, call me Young Master.

120
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,720
Didn't you say to only take one bite?

121
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,600
How many bites did you give me?

122
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:19,679
When I woke up this morning, I couldn't even stop my nose from bleeding.

123
00:08:19,679 --> 00:08:21,979
I was afraid it wouldn't be enough, so I took a few extra bites.

124
00:08:21,979 --> 00:08:25,520
Don't worry. My flesh is good.

125
00:08:34,719 --> 00:08:39,200
Don't worry, I'll recover tomorrow. I bit down a little hard.

126
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,899
You look like you've been chewed by a rat.

127
00:08:42,899 --> 00:08:46,640
Quite a few chunks are missing. It will look ugly.

128
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,159
You can stop now.

129
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:51,759
It's not visible to people normally. Just pretend that you don't know.

130
00:09:07,539 --> 00:09:10,339
Actually, you didn't need to do this for me.

131
00:09:11,939 --> 00:09:14,959
I know you are afraid that I would be hurt.

132
00:09:15,719 --> 00:09:17,319
It's fine.

133
00:09:17,319 --> 00:09:22,179
Just talk nicely to me, and I'll feel better.

134
00:09:22,179 --> 00:09:27,299
Such as... when did you start liking me?

135
00:09:29,699 --> 00:09:34,579
Like? This word is too superficial.

136
00:09:34,579 --> 00:09:36,659
I can't say it.

137
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,040
It's all right.

138
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:43,128
Anyway, I'm already used to you not saying what's in your heart.

139
00:09:43,128 --> 00:09:46,037
Just say nothing then.

140
00:09:46,037 --> 00:09:48,200
You've already eaten my flesh anyway.

141
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:51,999
That makes us merged into one, and we'll never be separated again.

142
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:57,039
I'm running away with a fugitive, of course, we'll stick together.

143
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:00,859
However, I have a question.

144
00:10:01,459 --> 00:10:05,080
After eating your flesh, can I live forever?

145
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:13,279
If you eat all of me, I still wouldn't know if you'll live forever.

146
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:15,840
But I'm pretty sure you won't if you eat only a little bit.

147
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,639
Jut a little bit?

148
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:19,679
You are quite generous.

149
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:21,810
You give it away on a whim.

150
00:10:23,219 --> 00:10:25,420
Then, I want a reward.

151
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:30,579
We're in broad daylight, restrain yourself.

152
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:37,939
Do you mean I can go wild once the lights are out?

153
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:42,020
If I had known, I should have kissed you a few more times when you were unconscious.

154
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:43,920
Ye Xi.

155
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:49,300
I'm simply astounded by Young Master's beauty.

156
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:52,740
Young Master, you are usually aloof and domineering.

157
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:57,099
When you are suddenly sickly and pitiful, I can't control myself.

158
00:10:57,099 --> 00:10:58,759
Have you forgotten?

159
00:10:58,759 --> 00:11:01,200
There are pursuers hunting us down.

160
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,679
You are already fully recovered.

161
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:05,859
With the two of us, we should be able to handle them.

162
00:11:05,859 --> 00:11:07,399
Where are we going now?

163
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,347
We'll look for Uncle Hui.

164
00:11:10,659 --> 00:11:12,359
Sure!

165
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,706
Are Uncle Hui and the others all right?

166
00:11:27,706 --> 00:11:30,465
They sneaked away by going under the hot spring.

167
00:11:30,465 --> 00:11:32,760
This is a mark left by Uncle Hui.

168
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:35,219
They should be on their way to Moon River.

169
00:11:35,219 --> 00:11:36,840
That is the Bai family clan's land.

170
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,639
They should be recuperating and taking temporary refuge there.

171
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:45,068
Why don't we also go to Moon River? It sounds so beautiful.

172
00:11:45,860 --> 00:11:50,380
Don't you feel that we're more like eloping than running for our lives?

173
00:11:50,380 --> 00:11:52,359
It does seem like it.

174
00:11:55,459 --> 00:11:58,100
There's a tea stand there. Let's go take a rest.

175
00:11:58,100 --> 00:11:59,130
All right.

176
00:11:59,130 --> 00:12:00,760
Go.

177
00:12:08,260 --> 00:12:11,220
Are you two tired? Take a seat. What would you like to drink?

178
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:12,080
Premium Jasmin tea.

179
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,690
Sure. Just a moment, please.

180
00:12:24,459 --> 00:12:26,999
How is it? Feel much better now?

181
00:12:26,999 --> 00:12:29,800
I'm very confident in my abilities.

182
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:33,679
I guarantee a mortal like you will feel totally refreshed.

183
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:37,639
A mortal will grow old and die eventually. It's unavoidable.

184
00:12:38,179 --> 00:12:40,561
That will be after 100 years.

185
00:12:41,319 --> 00:12:44,660
Compared to death, I think becoming senile is scarier.

186
00:12:44,660 --> 00:12:47,060
After many years, your appearance won't change.

187
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:51,030
But by then, my handsome looks would have faded away already.

188
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:53,639
I would rather die instead of being that way.

189
00:12:53,639 --> 00:12:57,540
You are so hopelessly narcissistic.

190
00:12:58,719 --> 00:13:03,620
That's why I can't do hard work in order to preserve my health.

191
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:06,505
I'd have to trouble you to work harder.

192
00:13:06,505 --> 00:13:08,260
Don't gaze at me like that.

193
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:11,800
When you risked your life for those men,

194
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:14,659
it cost you painstaking effort. I'm not asking you to do much.

195
00:13:14,659 --> 00:13:16,999
You just need to work a little harder.

196
00:13:18,779 --> 00:13:21,740
I thought you didn't mind it at all.

197
00:13:21,740 --> 00:13:25,515
Turns out you are so petty.

198
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:28,220
Your tea is ready.

199
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:34,990
Shopkeeper, I remember the previous shopkeeper was an old man.

200
00:13:35,439 --> 00:13:38,480
He recently went away on a trip. I've been here lately.

201
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,580
Enjoy the tea.

202
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,800
Go!

203
00:14:07,059 --> 00:14:09,620
Demoness, today is the day you die!

204
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:11,699
Hurry and hand over the Scripture of Materia Medica!

205
00:14:11,699 --> 00:14:15,620
The whole world knows you are undeniably a demoness.

206
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:18,140
That's why you can repeatedly live after death.

207
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:21,579
The Changliu Mountain is filled with people who want your head.

208
00:14:21,579 --> 00:14:24,848
The two of you won't be able to escape even if you had wings.

209
00:14:24,848 --> 00:14:27,659
Should I call you Young Master Bai or Valley Master Bai?

210
00:14:27,659 --> 00:14:31,659
You are asking for death when you partner with the demoness.

211
00:14:31,659 --> 00:14:36,359
Better to hand over the scripture now, and we'll let you die quickly.

212
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:39,520
In that case,

213
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:43,740
I'll let you see what a real demoness looks like.

214
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:45,440
Stop!

215
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,778
Surround them!

216
00:14:49,319 --> 00:14:52,180
Even the imperial court is after the demoness' head?

217
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:56,199
This is too much. Haven't you heard of first come first serve?

218
00:14:56,199 --> 00:14:58,057
I guess Cang Qi will be here soon.

219
00:14:58,057 --> 00:14:59,779
He has had people watching Fenghua Valley.

220
00:14:59,779 --> 00:15:02,260
It's impossible that he doesn't know about such a huge ruckus.

221
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:04,720
Are you saying he also wants my head?

222
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:08,300
He wants you. Any head that he wants would be mine.

223
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:12,320
He is insane. Let's get out of here before he shows up.

224
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:44,080
Ye Xi. After I've eaten so much of your flesh,

225
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,659
how are you doing?

226
00:15:45,659 --> 00:15:48,240
Didn't we agree not to talk about this anymore?

227
00:15:49,020 --> 00:15:51,880
I'm afraid that I can't digest it all.

228
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:56,300
Have you heard the saying that poor physical condition cannot absorb highly nutritional supplements?

229
00:15:56,300 --> 00:16:01,360
Sometimes, too many supplements will actually take lives than save lives.

230
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,840
Don't worry.

231
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:06,200
I'm here, and I'll definitely protect you to be safe and sound.

232
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:10,279
From now on, you don't need to fight. I'll protect you.

233
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:13,699
When you want to eat something, just tell me and I'll do as you wish.

234
00:16:13,699 --> 00:16:16,660
I will be virtuous and gentle.

235
00:16:16,660 --> 00:16:19,139
I won't ever talk back at you to upset you.

236
00:16:19,139 --> 00:16:21,479
I hope you'll recover very soon.

237
00:16:21,479 --> 00:16:26,565
There are still many things that we haven't done and many places we haven't visited.

238
00:16:26,565 --> 00:16:28,219
You're right.

239
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:32,501
We have so much in the past,

240
00:16:33,380 --> 00:16:35,900
but we'll have more in the future.

241
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:39,160
Actually, what Uncle Hui said is true.

242
00:16:39,579 --> 00:16:44,240
Perhaps he understood my feelings for you a lot earlier than I knew.

243
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:47,780
But you know it already.

244
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:52,179
Someone as prideful as I am won't easily admit it.

245
00:16:52,179 --> 00:16:54,460
I thought I could restrain myself.

246
00:16:56,140 --> 00:16:58,879
- Are you restraining yourself now?
- No.

247
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:02,679
Who was the one that disregarded everything in order to save me?

248
00:17:02,679 --> 00:17:04,799
He cared about what I ate and how I slept.

249
00:17:04,799 --> 00:17:07,702
He even played the flute on the rooftop for me.

250
00:17:07,702 --> 00:17:10,400
You didn't sugarcoat anything and scolded me constantly.

251
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,178
You appeared to greatly dislike me.

252
00:17:12,178 --> 00:17:16,480
Even though you aren't the perfect partner that I imagined, but it's fine.

253
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:20,263
What's important is that you love me.

254
00:17:21,519 --> 00:17:24,587
That's why you must change.

255
00:17:24,587 --> 00:17:28,340
If you need to say something, just say it. Don't suppress it.

256
00:17:28,340 --> 00:17:33,080
All right. But you should change too. Be a little more restrained.

257
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:35,999
A young lady shouldn't be so wild.

258
00:17:42,259 --> 00:17:45,540
We've already missed out so much time.

259
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:50,440
Going forward, I don't want to waste any minute and any second.

260
00:17:51,129 --> 00:17:57,379
I used to dream of having a home because I was too alone and wanted a companion.

261
00:17:58,130 --> 00:18:03,926
But now I've finally understood, not anyone can be my family.

262
00:18:03,926 --> 00:18:08,400
Only you can let me feel what it's like to be loved.

263
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:10,919
Therefore, promise me you'll get well.

264
00:18:10,919 --> 00:18:14,900
As long as you recover, I'll do whatever it takes.

265
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:17,780
If you really want to save me now,

266
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,879
there is one method.

267
00:18:23,019 --> 00:18:24,719
Look.

268
00:18:25,620 --> 00:18:29,219
There is a cliff after this forest.

269
00:18:29,219 --> 00:18:31,661
The Heavenly Bestowed Grass grows by the mountainside.
(aka Rhodiola Rosea)

270
00:18:31,661 --> 00:18:33,820
It's effective on me.

271
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:37,840
What is this herb that is more effective than I am?

272
00:18:38,459 --> 00:18:41,747
My congenital ailment needs to be treated with the right medicine.

273
00:18:41,747 --> 00:18:45,880
In this aspect, the Heavenly Bestowed Grass works better than ginseng.

274
00:18:46,979 --> 00:18:50,081
I already drew this plant here.

275
00:18:50,081 --> 00:18:51,900
Take the drawing to find it.

276
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:53,800
Be sure not to get the wrong one.

277
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,560
You'll recover once this is found?

278
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:05,880
- Yes.
- Good.

279
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:09,740
I'll go look for it right now. Wait for me. I'll definitely find it.

280
00:19:14,939 --> 00:19:19,739
Ye Xi, I know you are powerful.

281
00:19:19,739 --> 00:19:22,760
Be careful. Don't rush.

282
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:26,819
Come back soon. I want to eat the roast chicken that you cook.

283
00:21:03,010 --> 00:21:07,060
Heavenly Bestowed Grass... Heavenly Bestowed Grass?

284
00:21:07,060 --> 00:21:09,757
Does it have something to do with immortals and spirits?

285
00:21:09,757 --> 00:21:11,379
This isn't right.

286
00:21:11,379 --> 00:21:15,699
I am the king of herbs. How can it be more powerful than I am?

287
00:21:44,210 --> 00:21:46,759
"Life passes by like a flash of lightning."

288
00:21:46,759 --> 00:21:49,620
"The drawing is for missing a date with a beauty."

289
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:53,160
What does it mean?

290
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:56,419
How can he write a poem at this time? Can't he talk like a regular human?

291
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:03,452
He gave me a drawing.

292
00:22:03,452 --> 00:22:06,026
He told me to go by myself.

293
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,951
Bai Yue, you are a jerk!

294
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:16,309
If I want to go somewhere, is there anywhere I can't go in this world?

295
00:22:17,130 --> 00:22:19,818
So weird that he wants me to find this heavenly grass.

296
00:22:19,818 --> 00:22:22,201
He actually wants to abandon me.

297
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:30,919
Bai Yue! Bai Yue!

298
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:34,000
Bai Yue!

299
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:38,520
♫ I'm willing to pledge my life for unwavering love in the unpredictable future ♫

300
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:45,350
♫ Sadness and joy are silent in the vast sea while mountains and rivers have you in their hearts ♫

301
