307
00:23:26,820 --> 00:23:30,419
Bai Yue! Bai Yue!

308
00:23:30,419 --> 00:23:32,319
Bai Yue!

309
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:47,960
♫ Unrequited love leaps into reincarnation to pursue the beloved ♫

310
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:51,401
Bai Yue, come out!

311
00:23:51,401 --> 00:23:54,356
I know you are inside.

312
00:23:54,356 --> 00:23:57,821
Why are you abandoning me? Bai Yue!

313
00:23:57,821 --> 00:24:01,210
♫ I'll write a preface for you, a moment of fireworks ♫

