323
00:25:07,210 --> 00:25:16,280
♫ The years don't hold on to the memories ♫

324
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:39,100
Bai Yue,

325
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:41,250
I'm telling you.

326
00:25:41,250 --> 00:25:43,401
Don't dream of running away from me.

327
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:47,440
No matter where you hide, I will find you.

328
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:50,459
You won't ever get a chance to disappoint me in this whole lifetime.

329
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:54,791
Looks like you understand that poem.

330
00:25:57,970 --> 00:26:00,839
It's not that easy to see each other in the next life.

331
00:26:00,839 --> 00:26:04,532
Now that I'm committed to you, I won't give up.

332
00:26:06,010 --> 00:26:11,800
No matter what unspeakable secret you have, or how sickly you'll become, I won't mind at all.

333
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:16,924
As long as you stay alive, all is well.

334
00:26:18,540 --> 00:26:22,400
Besides, I have such strong power,

335
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:26,040
how can I not keep a mortal like you alive?

336
00:26:26,040 --> 00:26:28,580
Actually, I immediately wanted to stop you at that time.

337
00:26:28,580 --> 00:26:31,821
You don't need to lose parts of your real form for me.

338
00:26:33,020 --> 00:26:35,160
You can't save me.

339
00:26:35,930 --> 00:26:37,979
It's unavoidable.

340
00:26:37,979 --> 00:26:41,299
Impossible. I don't believe it.

341
00:26:41,860 --> 00:26:45,319
Are you hiding something from me? Tell me!

342
00:26:46,070 --> 00:26:48,179
Listen...

343
00:26:48,179 --> 00:26:50,423
Listen well.

344
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:53,899
You guessed it right.

345
00:26:53,899 --> 00:26:57,800
The Fenghua Valley Master is, in fact, a tomb keeper.

346
00:26:58,410 --> 00:27:04,659
Fenghua Valley is a mausoleum built by the first valley master as the joint tomb for him and his beloved woman.

347
00:27:05,860 --> 00:27:07,860
It is said that young woman

348
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:12,419
was fickle and left him.

349
00:27:12,419 --> 00:27:14,100
So he

350
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:18,179
sealed the tomb where the jade coffin was placed

351
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:21,379
and banned entry from then on.

352
00:27:21,379 --> 00:27:24,300
He built Fenghua Valley around it

353
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:28,919
to collect countless treasures and rare medical and martial arts books.

354
00:27:28,919 --> 00:27:32,040
He also demanded the successive valley masters guard the tomb for life.

355
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:37,320
They could enjoy all the treasures in the valley, but they could not fall in love with anyone.

356
00:27:37,320 --> 00:27:41,200
Otherwise, they would be cursed and die of heart exhaustion.

357
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:43,639
This rule

358
00:27:43,639 --> 00:27:48,519
has been verbally passed down through each valley master for generations. Even Uncle Hui doesn't know.

359
00:27:48,519 --> 00:27:50,640
I used to think

360
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:54,640
I would never fall in love.

361
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:58,299
But love came unexpectedly and made me fall deeply.

362
00:28:00,210 --> 00:28:01,919
Ye Xi,

363
00:28:02,580 --> 00:28:04,180
meeting you

364
00:28:05,350 --> 00:28:07,680
has made me very happy.

365
00:28:16,730 --> 00:28:19,380
Heart exhaustion?

366
00:28:21,410 --> 00:28:23,958
It hurts when I fall in love.

367
00:28:23,958 --> 00:28:26,384
It hurts even more when I fall more deeply in love.

368
00:28:27,359 --> 00:28:29,719
But I don't hurt anymore.

369
00:28:29,719 --> 00:28:31,820
I think I'm dying.

370
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:38,580
From inside the heart to my skin, this curse is extremely tormenting.

371
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:46,363
When did this curse get activated?

372
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:50,380
When I saw you climb out of the unmarked burial mounds,

373
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:58,098
I was pleasantly surprised, but it was also the first time that I felt unprecedented heartache.

374
00:28:58,098 --> 00:29:00,480
I pretended to be mean on purpose.

375
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:04,712
But the more I covered it up,

376
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:09,260
the more my feelings grew, and my heart ached even more.

377
00:29:12,939 --> 00:29:15,060
Love can take one's life.

378
00:29:16,079 --> 00:29:18,890
Who would willingly give up his life for this?

379
00:29:18,890 --> 00:29:21,960
♫ The wind is not lonely ♫

380
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:26,260
But if humans could control their feelings,

381
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:30,839
there wouldn't be so many people who are hindered by love.

382
00:29:32,039 --> 00:29:36,300
After thinking more about it, I decided to give up struggling against it.

383
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:38,518
If I had to die, I would just die.

384
00:29:38,518 --> 00:29:40,877
I didn't want you to go to Tang Sect.

385
00:29:41,462 --> 00:29:43,942
Moreover, I didn't want you to marry another person.

386
00:29:44,739 --> 00:29:46,920
I wanted to stop you.

387
00:29:47,939 --> 00:29:53,699
But I could feel my heartache getting worse every day.

388
00:29:53,699 --> 00:29:56,440
Apparently, the curse was becoming more ferocious.

389
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:59,460
I could only watch you leave.

390
00:30:00,559 --> 00:30:04,440
Because I knew you yearned for someone to grow old with,

391
00:30:06,140 --> 00:30:11,619
but I was unable to give you any promise, how was I qualified to stop you?

392
00:30:12,780 --> 00:30:17,480
After you left, I desperately searched for a solution to the curse.

393
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:20,179
I checked all the medical books,

394
00:30:20,179 --> 00:30:24,100
tried all kinds of medications, but it was useless.

395
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:30,630
As you can see now, I don't have much time left.

396
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:33,320
Ye Xi,

397
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:35,459
this is a curse.

398
00:30:35,459 --> 00:30:37,059
It's not an injury.

399
00:30:37,059 --> 00:30:39,400
You really can't save me.

400
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:41,482
Don't do anything silly anymore.

401
00:30:45,860 --> 00:30:47,860
Listen well.

402
00:30:48,799 --> 00:30:51,736
I'll say this only once in my life.

403
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:54,280
I love you.

404
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,380
I'll die without regrets.

405
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:04,527
You'd better not love me anymore.

406
00:31:05,259 --> 00:31:08,260
Why are you using your life to exchange for it?

407
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:11,010
Don't cry.

408
00:31:11,010 --> 00:31:17,190
♫ Dressing in light clothes, I've become forgotten in the horizon ♫

409
00:31:17,190 --> 00:31:20,480
♫ I can’t bear to go home again ♫

410
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:22,180
Don't cry.

411
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:28,599
♫ And I can’t seem to find your voice to accompany me ♫

412
00:31:28,599 --> 00:31:30,699
It's fine.

413
00:31:30,699 --> 00:31:32,179
Don't worry.

414
00:31:32,179 --> 00:31:34,610
I was too anxious when I came out.

415
00:31:34,610 --> 00:31:37,260
♫ My long-cherished wish has not been fulfilled, how can I leave you? ♫

416
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:40,939
You must always stay by my side.

417
00:31:40,939 --> 00:31:44,279
No matter how powerful I am, I can't live without you.

418
00:31:44,279 --> 00:31:46,990
You won't die. I won't allow it.

419
00:31:46,990 --> 00:31:48,980
♫ To find the warmth you left behind ♫

420
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:51,619
Even if someone is here to stop me,

421
00:31:51,619 --> 00:31:54,473
I'll just kill them.

422
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:57,590
♫ A gentle dream becomes reality magnifying the roads I’ve taken ♫

423
00:31:57,599 --> 00:32:02,539
If a god comes here to stop me, I'll just kill that god.

424
00:32:02,539 --> 00:32:05,799
If this is Heaven's will, I will change it.

425
00:32:05,799 --> 00:32:09,491
If it's a curse, I will break it.

426
00:32:09,491 --> 00:32:11,404
Fly up to heaven or dive down into the ground,

427
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:14,799
regardless of any obstacles from people or gods,

428
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:18,040
I will never give up.

429
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:24,060
♫ Unintentionally, like the trees and grass, I’m foolishly hoping for true love ♫

430
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:34,640
♫ I will wait for you for the rest of my life ♫

431
00:33:30,699 --> 00:33:33,016
Young Master, I know you can't stand the sun.

432
00:33:34,119 --> 00:33:35,919
I am curious.

433
00:33:36,559 --> 00:33:41,119
If you can conjure magic anytime, you must be able to turn a rock into gold.

434
00:33:43,039 --> 00:33:45,699
If I can really turn a rock into gold,

435
00:33:45,699 --> 00:33:47,820
when I first went to Bailu City,

436
00:33:47,820 --> 00:33:50,400
why didn't I know anything about money?

437
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:53,680
You didn't even want to pay for a bowl of noodles for me.

438
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:56,599
My skills are illusions. They fool people.

439
00:33:56,599 --> 00:33:58,299
I can't use them randomly.

440
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:01,599
It's good that you have this insight.

441
00:34:01,599 --> 00:34:04,619
But I have to remind you. It wasn't one bowl.

442
00:34:04,619 --> 00:34:07,000
To count accurately, there were six bowls.

443
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:13,980
You let me go to the city to nurture my body, didn't you?

444
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:16,215
You even bought a vailed hat for me.

445
00:34:16,840 --> 00:34:21,000
Were you afraid that I had many enemies who would recognize me and slaughter me?

446
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:25,200
If I had told you right then, would you have listened to me?

447
00:34:27,119 --> 00:34:33,220
If you could talk nicely, I think I would have loved you much sooner.

448
00:34:33,979 --> 00:34:36,619
But we would have lost a lot of fun from our arguments.

449
00:34:36,619 --> 00:34:38,800
I indeed didn't know how to speak well at that time.

450
00:34:39,539 --> 00:34:43,308
So you have poor eyesight, and I have a bad mouth.

451
00:34:44,619 --> 00:34:47,120
Aren't we quite the perfect match?

452
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:49,020
That's not right. Look at us.

453
00:34:49,619 --> 00:34:53,199
When you had white hair, I had black hair.

454
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:57,079
I have white hair now, but you have black hair.

455
00:34:57,740 --> 00:35:01,559
Does this mean that we won't grow old together?

456
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:09,380
- I don't even have the strength—
- Bai Yue.

457
00:35:10,393 --> 00:35:12,572
It isn't important if we can grow old together.

458
00:35:12,572 --> 00:35:16,780
If you had to die tomorrow, I would still want to be with you.

459
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:18,239
I've already told you.

460
00:35:18,239 --> 00:35:20,417
I don't care what kind of curse it is,

461
00:35:20,417 --> 00:35:23,140
I'm not afraid. Why are you afraid?

462
00:35:23,140 --> 00:35:25,280
I'm not afraid of the curse.

463
00:35:27,119 --> 00:35:30,919
I'm afraid that if I die, you would be sad.

464
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:39,705
Don't worry about whether I'll be sad.

465
00:35:39,705 --> 00:35:42,543
As long as you can stay with me,

466
00:35:42,543 --> 00:35:47,193
even if it's one day of happiness, I'd gladly exchange my whole life for it.

467
00:36:03,019 --> 00:36:04,919
He is coming.

468
00:36:05,740 --> 00:36:07,822
You can't use your martial arts skill now.

469
00:36:07,822 --> 00:36:10,735
I can use my power to conceal both of us.

470
00:36:13,079 --> 00:36:15,119
Don't use your power randomly anymore.

471
00:36:15,860 --> 00:36:17,760
I know a way.

472
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,880
Sooner or later we have to face them.

473
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:21,280
What is this way?

474
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:23,839
In a while, don't get impulsive no matter what happens.

475
00:36:23,839 --> 00:36:26,136
- Help me get up.
- All right.

476
00:36:38,130 --> 00:36:43,430
”Waiting” - Li Hongyi

477
00:36:43,430 --> 00:36:48,920
♫ How many stories have you heard of the Mortal World? ♫

478
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:55,190
♫ Dressing in light clothes, I've become forgotten in the horizon ♫

479
00:36:55,190 --> 00:37:00,920
♫ I can’t bear to go home again ♫

480
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:06,490
♫ And I can’t seem to find your voice to accompany me ♫

481
00:37:06,490 --> 00:37:12,210
♫ The sound of the melodious song leisurely stirs up the past ♫

482
00:37:12,210 --> 00:37:18,100
♫ My long-cherished wish has not been fulfilled, how can I leave you? ♫

483
00:37:18,100 --> 00:37:24,040
♫ How could destiny take me back to that city? ♫

484
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:29,800
♫ To find the warmth you left behind ♫

485
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:35,680
♫ A gentle dream becomes reality magnifying the roads I’ve taken ♫

486
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:41,610
♫ Laughing and sighing in this life, why bother asking if I’d be interested in it again? ♫

487
00:37:41,610 --> 00:37:47,460
♫ Why is there someone willing to wait without knowing the pain and resentment? ♫

488
00:37:47,460 --> 00:37:53,220
♫ It’s hard to tell stories of the past ♫

